(12747, 2730, 128, 'My name is Avdhesh Upadhyay. I am 37 years old and currently based in Delhi.\r\nMy Experience:\r\n•	Worked at Bhagwati Hospital (100-bedded, NABH accredited, Rohini, Delhi) as an OT/CSSD Technician for approximately 1 year (experience letter available)2010-2011.\r\n•	Worked at RG Stone Urology and Laparoscopic Hospital (a unit of RG Scientific Enterprises Pvt. Ltd.), Rajouri Garden, Delhi from June 2011 to December 2012 (1.5 years experience with experience letter).\r\n•	After 2013, I worked for around 10 years as a computer operator in jewellery showrooms due to personal reasons.\r\nMy Education:\r\n•	Completed a 9-month OT/CSSD Assistant course (theory and practical) from Safdarjung Hospital (2009–2010).\r\n•	Completed 12th CBSE (Commerce) in 2007.\r\n•	Currently in the final year of online distance learning B.Com from Subharti University, which will be completed in September.', NULL, 'Read', 'Yes', '2026-03-23 15:43:25', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
(12748, 2730, 128, 'I would like to inquire about opportunities to return to the healthcare field, specifically for caregiver or healthcare jobs abroad.\r\nI am now fully motivated to return to the healthcare sector and am ready to refresh my skills if required.\r\nIf opportunities in the healthcare field are limited, I am open to working in other sectors and am willing to learn and adapt to new roles.\r\n\r\nI would like your guidance regarding:\r\n•	Suitable countries for my profile \r\n•	Required qualifications or certifications\r\n•	Complete process for caregiver/healthcare jobs abroad\r\nIf possible, I would also like to discuss my profile in more detail over a call at your convenience.\r\nThank you for your time and assistance. I look forward to your response.\r\nWarm regards,\r\nAvdhesh Upadhyay\r\nDelhi, India\r\navdhesh.ot@gmail.com\r\n8851238253', NULL, 'Read', 'Yes', '2026-03-23 15:43:51', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL),
